    ${misc:Depends}
Description: DuckBotOS base system — required for all install modes
 This is the base package that all DuckBotOS install modes depend on.
 It provides the minimal Ubuntu 24.04 system with:
 - Ubuntu Server base + standard utils
 - Python 3 + pip (Hermes, OpenClaw, skills)
 - Node.js 18+ (OpenClaw)
 - Weston compositor (kiosk shell)
 - Audio support (voice features)
 - Basic system monitoring and security tools
 .
 This package is Essential and Priority=required — it cannot be removed.